nodes.text: "Wrong-Way" Wint was a male Clantaani who belonged to a gang of criminals in Mos Espa led by Longo Two-Guns during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. Jabba the Hutt placed a bounty on Wint for skimming profits from a "legitimate" protection agency on Mos Espa. He was captured by Jango Fett who claimed the bounty just after the Battle of Naboo.
